Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.04,0:00:37.94,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,而是用肉眼观测广阔的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.10,0:00:40.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,快看啊蓝
